  <brief_title>Japanese Study Evaluating the Effects of Telithromycin in Children With Acute Otitis Media</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Safety, Efficacy, Pharmacokinetics, and Acceptability of HMR3647 20 mg/kg qd for 5 Days With Acute Otitis Media (AOM) in Children (Multicenter, Open Label, Non Comparative Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
