    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are weighing 40 kg or less. If female, premenarchal status is required.

          -  Subjects with signs of infection according to middle ear signs and general signs or
             symptoms such as otalgia, fever, sleep disturbance, irritability, inconsolability.

        The above information is not intended to contain all considerations relevant to a patient's
        potential participation in a clinical trial.
      </textblock>
